  N4 --> N5[PB: Notification + UI Screen (dashboard/report) - Notify stakeholders and surface dashboards/recommendations]
  N5 --> Z1[Outcome: Tighter cost control and higher contract utilization leading to lower freight COGS, fewer service exceptions, improved working capital through timely dispute/claim handling, and measurable EBITDA uplift from optimized LSP mix and penalty recovery.]
  N3 -->|Performance deviation within auto-act...| B1[Automated routing change and carrier ramp executed via Remote Functions; update spend and KPIs in Subject Areas]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Fast correction with no manual intervention; reduced service impact and minimal cost delta]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N3 -->|Deviation exceeds tolerance or contra...| B2[Create CWB Lifecycle case with Agent Team summary, attach RCA and financial impact; route to Procurement + Legal for approval]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: Human-in-the-loop review, potential penalty recovery or negotiated remediation; audit trail preserved]
  O2 --> End[End]
  N3 -->|Key input data quality or missing con...| B3[Process Builder triggers Data Quality & Validation rules in STREAMS, pauses decision, notifies data stewards and queues Agent Team to extract/interpret missing clauses]
